org.mxupdate.update.util
Class AdminProperty_mxJPO

java.lang.Object
  org.mxupdate.update.util.AdminProperty_mxJPO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<AdminProperty_mxJPO>
public class AdminProperty_mxJPO
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<AdminProperty_mxJPO>

Property with name, value and referenced administration type. The kind of property (with reference, with value, ...) is stored as flag. A property is only used within administration objects (not business objects).

compareTo

public int compareTo(AdminProperty_mxJPO _toCompare)

Compares this administration property instance with _toCompare administration property. The algorithm uses

  • refAdminType
  • refAdminName
  • name
  • value
in the defined order to compare this administration property against _toCompare. A null value is always lower than a non null value.

Specified by:
compareTo in interface Comparable<AdminProperty_mxJPO>
Parameters:
_toCompare - admin property instance which must be compared to
Returns:
"0" if both administration properties are equal; "1" if greater; otherwise "-1"
